  "title": "杏仁体可能涉及到奖励新奇的输入",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"fmfwf9yY\"> 一些对奖励视觉刺激有反应的杏仁体神经元也会对相对新奇的视觉刺激有反应。并且它们可能实现新奇刺激所具有的奖励价值（FAW Wilson &amp; ET Rolls, in preparation; Rolls 1999a, 2000b）</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"vO739ddB\">引用的摘录来自以下<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/References\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">参考资料</a>：</p><p data-pid=\"Cj-G8Ke8\">标题：<b>大脑中的记忆系统</b></p><p data-pid=\"bxZ-iI_r\">作者：Edmund T. Rolls</p><p data-pid=\"EY5oEjJL\">链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//docplayer.net/46038895-Memory-systems-in-the-brain.html\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://</span><span class=\"visible\">docplayer.net/46038895-</span><span class=\"invisible\">Memory-systems-in-the-brain.html</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"CBhV-R1d\">反向链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Pleasure_of_learning\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">学习的乐趣</a><sup data-text=\"学习的乐趣\" data-url=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/429432467/answer/1578551193\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"89CLKhui\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Amygdala_may_be_involved_in_rewarding_novel_input\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Amygdala may be involved in rewarding novel input - supermemo.guru</a><br/>本<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/References\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">参考资料</a>用于支持<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//